+Examples:
+1. Upload automake-1.8.2b.tar.gz and automake-1.8.2b.tar.bz2 to two sites:
+  gnupload --to sources.redhat.com:~ftp/pub/automake \\
+           --to alpha.gnu.org:automake \\
+           automake-1.8.2b.tar.gz automake-1.8.2b.tar.bz2
+
