+automake-1.8.2b.tar.bz2 to automake-latest.tar.bz2 on both sites:
+
+  gnupload --to sources.redhat.com:~ftp/pub/automake \\
+           --to alpha.gnu.org:automake \\
+           --symlink automake-1.8.2b.tar.gz automake-latest.tar.gz \\
